Sprint 5 Echipa Furnica Backend API

GET /recurring
- returns all recurring payments

Sample response : {"total": 500,
                   "list": [
                        {"id":1, "catId":1, "amount": 300, "date":1-2-2016},
                        {"id":2, "catId":4, "amount": -200, "date":2-2-2016}
                    ]}

Parameters :
   type=all (default) , positive , negative

GET /recurring/{id}
- returns a recurring payment by id

POST /recurring/{id}
 - adds a recurring payment

PUT /recurring/{id}
 - edits a recurring payment

DELETE /recurring/{id}
 - deletes a recurring payment


CATEGORY

 GET /category
 - returns all categories

 Sample response : {
                    "list": [
                         {"id":1, "name":"Food", type="expense", "limit":300},
                         {"id":2, "name":"Transportation", type="expense", limit":100},
                         {"id":2, "name":"Salary", type="income", limit":0}
                     ]}

 Parameters :
    type="all" (default)
    type="positive"
    type="negative"

 GET /recurring/{id}
 - returns a recurring payment by id

 POST /recurring
  - adds a recurring payment

 PUT /recurring/{id}
  - edits a recurring payment

 DELETE /recurring/{id}
  - deletes a recurring payment





